      <p class='mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>
        In addition to scholarships, consider these financial aid options:
      </p>
      <ul class='mt-4 space-y-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300'>
        <li>
          <strong>Grants:</strong> Funds that do not require repayment, typically awarded based on financial
          need.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Work-Study Programs:</strong> Part-time job opportunities offered by universities to
          help students cover educational expenses.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Student Loans:</strong> Loans that must be repaid with interest; explore government
          and private loan options carefully.
        </li>
      </ul>

